## **üîó CROSS-PLATFORM INTEGRATION WORKFLOWS**

### **ATLVS ‚Üî COMPVSS Integration**
- [ ] Automated project creation in COMPVSS when deal closes in ATLVS
- [ ] Bidirectional budget sync (planned in ATLVS, actual in COMPVSS)
- [ ] Asset availability checking from ATLVS inventory when planning in COMPVSS
- [ ] Crew assignment with automatic payroll data flow to ATLVS
- [ ] Expense submission in COMPVSS auto-routing to ATLVS AP
- [ ] Production hours tracked in COMPVSS flowing to ATLVS payroll
- [ ] Vendor invoice from COMPVSS matching to PO in ATLVS
- [ ] Risk and compliance alerts from COMPVSS to ATLVS dashboards
- [ ] Project status updates syncing to ATLVS portfolio view
- [ ] Change orders in COMPVSS triggering budget revisions in ATLVS
- [ ] Asset damage reports in COMPVSS updating maintenance schedules in ATLVS
- [ ] Project completion in COMPVSS triggering financial closeout in ATLVS
- [ ] Resource allocation conflicts flagged across both systems
- [ ] Client satisfaction scores from COMPVSS updating CRM in ATLVS

### **ATLVS ‚Üî GVTEWAY Integration**
- [ ] Client CRM data in ATLVS syncing to guest profiles in GVTEWAY
- [ ] Ticket revenue and merchandise sales flowing to ATLVS GL
- [ ] Inventory levels syncing between ATLVS asset management and GVTEWAY merchandise
- [ ] Marketing spend tracked in GVTEWAY reporting to ATLVS finance
- [ ] Customer lifetime value calculations combining ATLVS CRM and GVTEWAY purchase data
- [ ] Payment processing settlement from GVTEWAY to ATLVS accounting
- [ ] Vendor performance from GVTEWAY events updating ATLVS vendor database
- [ ] Artist booking data in ATLVS creating events in GVTEWAY
- [ ] Financial reconciliation between platforms with discrepancy alerts
- [ ] Tax reporting combining data from both platforms

### **COMPVSS ‚Üî GVTEWAY Integration**
- [ ] Event details (date, time, venue, lineup) syncing from COMPVSS to GVTEWAY
- [ ] Production schedule updates pushing real-time notifications via GVTEWAY
- [ ] Capacity and venue layout from COMPVSS determining ticket inventory in GVTEWAY
- [ ] Seating charts created in COMPVSS becoming ticketing maps in GVTEWAY
- [ ] Show day updates and delays in COMPVSS alerting guests via GVTEWAY
- [ ] Production photos and content in COMPVSS feeding guest memory galleries in GVTEWAY
- [ ] Guest services directory in COMPVSS accessible through GVTEWAY app
- [ ] Incident reports in COMPVSS affecting guest experience triggering GVTEWAY communications
- [ ] Access control data from GVTEWAY (tickets scanned) feeding COMPVSS show reports
- [ ] VIP guest lists from GVTEWAY syncing to COMPVSS backstage management
- [ ] Merchandise sales data from GVTEWAY informing COMPVSS inventory needs
- [ ] Weather alerts in COMPVSS pushing to GVTEWAY guest notifications
- [ ] Parking and transportation info from COMPVSS displaying in GVTEWAY
- [ ] Set times and curfew in COMPVSS publishing to GVTEWAY event pages

### **Tri-Platform Workflows**
- [ ] New client inquiry ‚Üí ATLVS CRM ‚Üí Won deal ‚Üí COMPVSS project ‚Üí GVTEWAY event listing
- [ ] Asset purchase in ATLVS ‚Üí Available in COMPVSS ‚Üí Used at event ‚Üí Guest sees in GVTEWAY experience
- [ ] Crew hired in ATLVS ‚Üí Assigned in COMPVSS ‚Üí Creates content ‚Üí Appears in GVTEWAY
- [ ] Marketing campaign in GVTEWAY ‚Üí Tracked in ATLVS ‚Üí Informs production needs in COMPVSS
- [ ] Ticket sales in GVTEWAY ‚Üí Revenue in ATLVS ‚Üí Capacity planning in COMPVSS
- [ ] Guest feedback in GVTEWAY ‚Üí Issue logged in COMPVSS ‚Üí Vendor rating updated in ATLVS
- [ ] Unified reporting dashboard pulling KPIs from all three platforms
- [ ] Single sign-on (SSO) across all three platforms
- [ ] Universal notification system across platforms
- [ ] Cross-platform search functionality

